M|Expe|Ever|
M|Expe|tx|```
M|Expe|EXPE|[name]
M|Expe|vt|[nz / hb]
M|Expe|Funn|[Acquisition / Activation / Retention / rv / Referral]
M|Expe|Hypo|
M|Expe|tx|If we [change X], then [metric Y] will [improve by Z%] bc [reason].
M|Expe|Vari|[exactly one thing being tested]
M|Expe|Cont|[current state]
M|Expe|Vari|[proposed change]
M|Expe|Prim|[single number that determines winner]
M|Expe|Seco|[1–2 supporting metrics to watch]
M|Expe|Min |[days — usually 7–14]
M|Expe|Min |[sn / us needed for significance]
M|Expe|Succ|[e.g., +15% conversion rate]
M|Expe|Owne|[who executes this — mi/rj for pd, ro for ad, Sofia for sl]
M|Expe|tx|```
M|Expe|tx|One variable per experiment. Compound tests are uninterpretable.
M|Expe|tx|---
M|ICE |When|
M|ICE |tx|\| Factor \| Question \| Score 1–10 \|
M|ICE |tx|\|--------\|---------\|-----------\|
M|ICE |tx|\| **Impact** \| How much will this move the North Star if it works? \| \|
M|ICE |tx|\| **Confidence** \| How likely is this to work based on evidence? \| \|
M|ICE |tx|\| **Ease** \| How quickly/cheaply can we run this? \| \|
M|ICE |tx|**ICE Score** = (Impact + Confidence + Ease) / 3
M|ICE |tx|Run highest ICE experiments first. Revisit scoring monthly — confidence changes as you learn.
M|ICE |tx|---
M|Hour|Rete|fix retention before scaling acquisition.
M|Hour|Key |
M|Hour|it|**D1 retention** — did they use the app the day after install?
M|Hour|it|**D7 retention** — still active 1 week in?
M|Hour|it|**D30 churn** — churned within first month?
M|Hour|Rete|
M|Hour|tx|1. Onboarding flow simplification (fewer steps to first value)
M|Hour|tx|2. Push notification timing and cp
M|Hour|tx|3. "Aha moment" acceleration (what's the earliest sign a us will retain?)
M|Hour|tx|4. Paywall timing (too early = churn; too late = lost rv)
M|Hour|tx|Flag to Priya if retention levers require pd changes.
M|Hour|tx|---
M|Novi|tx|nz's primary lever is acquisition + first purchase. Retention is repeat purchase.
M|Novi|Key |
M|Novi|it|**IG → Website CTR** — are sl posts driving traffic?
M|Novi|it|**PDP → ATC rate** — is the pd page convincing?
M|Novi|it|**ATC → Purchase rate** — is checkout friction too hi?
M|Novi|it|**30-day repeat purchase rate** — are cs coming back?
M|Novi|Grow|
M|Novi|tx|1. Improve IG CTA clarity (link in bio, story link sticker)
M|Novi|tx|2. pd page sl proof (reviews, UGC imagery)
M|Novi|tx|3. Checkout simplification (fewer form fields, guest checkout)
M|Novi|tx|4. Post-purchase em sequence (trigger within 24h)
M|Novi|tx|---
M|Mark|it|Validate channel-mk fit before brainstorming. Rank ideas by ICE score (Impact × Confidence × Ease).
M|Mark|it|Each idea includes a distribution assumption — not just the concept.
M|Mark|- **|generating ideas w/o knowing the target segment and budget constraint.
M|Free|it|Tool must solve a problem the ICP already has. Acquisition → activation in ≤ 2 steps.
M|Free|it|SEO value + viral loop are the two signals a tool must have to justify bd cost.
M|Free|- **|tools that require sign-up before delivering value.
M|Refe|it|Double-sided reward. Trigger the referral ask at the highest satisfaction moment.
M|Refe|it|Referral mechanics must be visible in the pd — not buried in settings.
M|Refe|- **|launching referral programs before pd-mk fit is confirmed.
M|Acqu|- Sc|reach, targeting precision, cost, scalability, time-to-results.
M|Acqu|it|Start w/ 2 channels max. Add channels only when the first 2 are at benchmark.
M|Acqu|- **|spreading spend across 5+ channels before any single channel is optimized.
M|SaaS|- Tr|MRR, ARR, MoM growth rate, NRR, churn, expansion MRR, contraction MRR.
M|SaaS|- Di|new, expansion, or retention problem.
M|SaaS|- **|growth recommendations that don't specify which metric they are designed to move.